    <section name="Goto a Folder">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to get to a folder, to add or change content in it.</span>

   <div class='screenshot'>
     <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M9/contribs/goto_folder.png" alt='Goto folder screenshot'/>
     <p>
        Clicking on the name 'newspaper', to go to that folder, to see the 
        <a href='../concepts/document.html'>documents</a> in it.      
    </p>
   </div>

   <p>
      In the <a href='../concepts/content_navigation_panel.html'>content navigation panel</a>,
      within the <a href='../concepts/document_slider.html'>document slider</a>, the names of all folders
      for <a href='../concepts/document.html'>documents</a> are shown.
      <span class='add'>Document about navigation in folder tree and reference from here.</span>
   </p>
   <p>
      Clicking on a foldername will bring you to the folder, to see its contents.
      The contents of the folder will appear in the <a href='../concepts/content_listing_panel.html'></a>
      content listing panel.
   </p>

